text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This obsoletes IRM 4.61.10, International Examination Guidelines, Foreign Tax Credit.

This IRM is obsolete, as the content is informational and not instructions to staff, in accordance with IRM 4.51.2, LB&I Administrative Guidance, Supplemental Guidance and Informational Resources. The International Knowledge Base provides informational resources for Foreign Tax Credits – Busi- ness (under Business Outbound) and Foreign Tax Credits – Individual (under Individual Outbound). Information can also be obtained by contacting the FTC Practice Network teams.
